a Information Technology Co., Ltd.; HRBP
Responsibilities:
1.Supporting line managers as a process consult in HR regular activities, including performance review, talent management, and salary review, etc.;
2.Coordinate with HR Services, Talent Acquisition, Learning teams to drive related HR initiatives;
3.Handling other HR administrative tasks assigned.
b Data analyst
Responsibilities:
1.Leading analysis of Web, mobile and WeChat user data;
2.Performing regular audit and performance analysis of product and user data;
3.Delivering client reports to communicate findings and analysis.
c  HR Generalist
Responsibilities:
Responsible for HR routines for daily HR topics in terms of on-boarding administration, employee contract management, employee profile and employee relocation support, exiting administration etc.
d HR Manager
Responsibilities:
1.Building core team by recruiting technicians, sales and operation staff;
2.Setting up basic human resources management system;
3.Searching and contacting potential suppliers, and building further cooperation.
2014.09-2015.07 Brecruit China; Manufacturing Department; Recruiter
Responsibilities:
Mainly responsible for recruiting candidates ranging from senior engineers to directors, functions covering research, sales, and management etc., for clients in auto and automation industry. 

Skills & Characteristics 
1.Professional in Microsoft Word, Excel, and PowerPoint, proficient in SPSS and Photoshop, eager to learn and able to master new skills fast;
2.Passionate about recruitment job, and skilled in using different recruitment tools;
3.Knowledge of HR policies, HR procedures and tools;
4.Enjoying and good at communicating with people, and fluent in English.
